nodes.text: The Caluula Resistance was a resistance movement operating on Caluula in 29 ABY, hoping to rid the planet of the occupying Yuuzhan Vong. The Rodian Sasso was a member who cooperated with Ferfer of the Ryn Network in hooking up with Team Meloque of the Galactic Federation of Free Alliances, who were on a mission to destroy the world's yammosk.
